text: Yvette Prieto (born March 26, 1979) is an American model of cuban decent. Prieto is the wife of basketball legend Michael Jordan. She has modeled for designer Alexander Wang. She has also appeared in the documentary Cuba: An Island Apart as herself. Prieto was born in Cuba to Carlos and Maria Prieto. She grew up in Miami. Prieto married Jordan in April 27, 2013, at Bethesda-by- the-Sea Episcopal Church. The couple have twin daughters Ysabel and Victoria. They were born on February 9, 2014. ==References== category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:models from Florida
